P(Ai|Ii) = 2/4 = 0.50

P(Ai|Ij) = 5/99996 = 5.0 * 10^-5


                       (2.5 * 10^-4) * (5.0^-10) 	                
BDR =  ------------------------------------------------------------- = 0.7143
        (2.5 * 10^-4) * (5.0^-10) + (9.9975 * 10^-1) * (5.0 * 10^-5)



